and the shame and--

1487
01:31:48,870 --> 01:31:51,270
Just pushes up at my gut
like vomit.

1488
01:31:51,272 --> 01:31:53,212
It's just...

1489
01:31:53,207 --> 01:31:56,837
I can't keep it down.

1490
01:31:56,844 --> 01:31:59,084
And I think...

1491
01:31:59,646 --> 01:32:02,976
