1546
01:34:56,356 --> 01:34:59,316
Just give it to me
for a while.

1547
01:35:04,230 --> 01:35:05,730
I'll be okay.

1548
01:35:05,733 --> 01:35:08,473
I won't do anything stupid.

1549
01:35:12,839 --> 01:35:15,009
[sighs]

